#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.54"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.54:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.54:0.2"
msgid "6. Puññābhisandavagga"
msgstr "6. Overflowing Merit"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.54:0.3"
msgid "54. Dutiyasaṃvāsasutta"
msgstr "54. Living Together (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.54:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, saṃvāsā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are four ways of living together."

msgctxt "an4.54:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.54:1.3"
msgid ""
"Chavo chavāya saddhiṃ saṃvasati, chavo deviyā saddhiṃ saṃvasati, devo "
"chavāya saddhiṃ saṃvasati, devo deviyā saddhiṃ saṃvasati."
msgstr ""
"~A male zombie living with a female zombie; ~a male zombie living with a "
"goddess; ~a god living with a female zombie; ~a god living with a goddess."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.60"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.54:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, chavo chavāya saddhiṃ saṃvasati."
msgstr "And how does a male zombie live with a female zombie?"

msgctxt "an4.54:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, sāmiko hoti pāṇātipātī adinnādāyī kāmesumicchācārī musāvādī "
"pisuṇavāco pharusavāco samphappalāpī abhijjhālu byāpannacitto micchādiṭṭhiko "
"dussīlo pāpadhammo maccheramalapariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati "
"akkosakaparibhāsako samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when the husband kills living creatures, steals, commits sexual "
"misconduct; he uses speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or nonsensical; "
"and he’s covetous, malicious, and has wrong view. He’s unethical, of bad "
"character, living at home with his heart full of the stain of stinginess, "
"abusing and insulting ascetics and brahmins."

msgctxt "an4.54:2.3"
msgid ""
"bhariyāpissa hoti pāṇātipātinī adinnādāyinī kāmesumicchācārinī musāvādinī "
"pisuṇavācā pharusavācā samphappalāpinī abhijjhālunī byāpannacittā "
"micchādiṭṭhikā dussīlā pāpadhammā maccheramalapariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ "
"ajjhāvasati akkosikaparibhāsikā samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ."
msgstr "And the wife is also … unethical, of bad character …"

msgctxt "an4.54:2.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, chavo chavāya saddhiṃ saṃvasati."
msgstr "That’s how a male zombie lives with a female zombie."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.54:3.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, chavo deviyā saddhiṃ saṃvasati?"
msgstr "And how does a male zombie live with a goddess?"

msgctxt "an4.54:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, sāmiko hoti pāṇātipātī … pe … micchādiṭṭhiko dussīlo "
"pāpadhammo maccheramalapariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati "
"akkosakaparibhāsako samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ;"
msgstr "It’s when the husband … is unethical, of bad character …"

msgctxt "an4.54:3.3"
msgid ""
"bhariyā khvassa hoti pāṇātipātā paṭiviratā adinnādānā paṭiviratā "
"kāmesumicchācārā paṭiviratā musāvādā paṭiviratā pisuṇāya vācāya paṭiviratā "
"pharusāya vācāya paṭiviratā samphappalāpā paṭiviratā anabhijjhālunī "
"abyāpannacittā sammādiṭṭhikā sīlavatī kalyāṇadhammā vigatamalamaccherena "
"cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati anakkosikaparibhāsikā samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"But the wife doesn’t kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, "
"lie, or use alcoholic drinks that cause negligence. She’s ethical, of good "
"character, living at home with her heart rid of the stain of stinginess, not "
"abusing and insulting ascetics and brahmins."

msgctxt "an4.54:3.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, chavo deviyā saddhiṃ saṃvasati."
msgstr "That’s how a male zombie lives with a goddess."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.54:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, devo chavāya saddhiṃ saṃvasati?"
msgstr "And how does a god live with a female zombie?"

msgctxt "an4.54:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, sāmiko hoti pāṇātipātā paṭivirato adinnādānā paṭivirato "
"kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato musāvādā paṭivirato pisuṇāya vācāya paṭivirato "
"pharusāya vācāya paṭivirato samphappalāpā paṭivirato anabhijjhālu "
"abyāpannacitto sammādiṭṭhiko sīlavā kalyāṇadhammo vigatamalamaccherena "
"cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati anakkosakaparibhāsako samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ;"
msgstr "It’s when the husband … is ethical, of good character …"

msgctxt "an4.54:4.3"
msgid ""
"bhariyā khvassa hoti pāṇātipātinī … pe … micchādiṭṭhikā dussīlā pāpadhammā "
"maccheramalapariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati akkosikaparibhāsikā "
"samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ."
msgstr "But the wife … is unethical, of bad character …"

msgctxt "an4.54:4.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, devo chavāya saddhiṃ saṃvasati."
msgstr "That’s how a god lives with a female zombie."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.54:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, devo deviyā saddhiṃ saṃvasati?"
msgstr "And how does a god live with a goddess?"

msgctxt "an4.54:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, sāmiko hoti pāṇātipātā paṭivirato … pe … sammādiṭṭhiko "
"sīlavā kalyāṇadhammo vigatamalamaccherena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati "
"anakkosakaparibhāsako samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ;"
msgstr "It’s when the husband … is ethical, of good character …"

msgctxt "an4.54:5.3"
msgid ""
"bhariyāpissa hoti pāṇātipātā paṭiviratā … pe … sammādiṭṭhikā sīlavatī "
"kalyāṇadhammā vigatamalamaccherena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati "
"anakkosikaparibhāsikā samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ."
msgstr "And the wife is also … ethical, of good character …"

msgctxt "an4.54:5.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, devo deviyā saddhiṃ saṃvasati."
msgstr "That’s how a god lives with a goddess."

msgctxt "an4.54:5.5"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro saṃvāsāti."
msgstr "These are the four ways of living together.” …"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.61"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an4.54:6.1"
msgid "Ubho ca honti dussīlā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:6.2"
msgid "kadariyā paribhāsakā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:6.3"
msgid "Te honti jānipatayo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:6.4"
msgid "chavā saṃvāsamāgatā."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an4.54:7.1"
msgid "Sāmiko hoti dussīlo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:7.2"
msgid "kadariyo paribhāsako;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:7.3"
msgid "Bhariyā sīlavatī hoti,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:7.4"
msgid "vadaññū vītamaccharā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:7.5"
msgid "Sāpi devī saṃvasati,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:7.6"
msgid "chavena patinā saha."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an4.54:8.1"
msgid "Sāmiko sīlavā hoti,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:8.2"
msgid "vadaññū vītamaccharo;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:8.3"
msgid "Bhariyā hoti dussīlā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:8.4"
msgid "kadariyā paribhāsikā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:8.5"
msgid "Sāpi chavā saṃvasati,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:8.6"
msgid "devena patinā saha."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an4.54:9.1"
msgid "Ubho saddhā vadaññū ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:9.2"
msgid "saññatā dhammajīvino;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:9.3"
msgid "Te honti jānipatayo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:9.4"
msgid "aññamaññaṃ piyaṃvadā."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an4.54:10.1"
msgid "Atthāsaṃ pacurā honti,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:10.2"
msgid "phāsukaṃ upajāyati;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:10.3"
msgid "Amittā dummanā honti,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:10.4"
msgid "ubhinnaṃ samasīlinaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an4.54:11.1"
msgid "Idha dhammaṃ caritvāna,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:11.2"
msgid "samasīlabbatā ubho;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:11.3"
msgid "Nandino devalokasmiṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.54:11.4"
msgid "modanti kāmakāmino”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.54:11.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
